info.name: pom pom purin youtube logo
info.description:
changes the youtube logo to a purin gif!
if anyone has suggestions on more purin (or other sanrio) stuff i should make, please comment !!

extra !!
if u want to have a purin cursor, download custom curser here:
https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/custom-cursor-for-chrome/ogdlpmhglpejoiomcodnpjnfgcpmgale/related?hl=en-US

then, download the purin cursor here: 
https://custom-cursor.com/en/collection/sanrio/pompompurin-dog

i'm not sure how i could add that specific cursor into the style so i thought i'd just give u this! be aware that this cursor does not only add to youtube, but also other sites!
